{"tid":600062,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人知破曉呢首歌講緊咩？","createTime":"2018-03-21T04:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T14:13:55.000Z","uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0826570b2c0e61f8d0e351fd28cfab17591d6163","tid":600062,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"林憶蓮<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/you2RoU0ILI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fyou2RoU0ILI&d=5gUHD5hnZIOw1Z4EuMo5TDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7a2cf4bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/you2RoU0ILI</a><br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6_63A0nY5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6_63A0nY5c&d=5gUHD5hnZIOw1Z4EuMo5TDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5046ba97\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6_63A0nY5c</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞<br />\n遺棄的聲音又響起了　遺棄的感覺偏剩下多少<br />\n不聽不觸摸不痛楚　懶看懶記憶懶問我<br />\n今天得到的叫什麼　管不了<br />\n<br />\n天　亦天天的了　地　天天的了<br />\n心也未能料　我已再不渺小<br />\n讓昨天一朝了　或且某月某日某宵我倦了 *<br />\n<br />\n人有幾多天拾起改變<br />\n人有幾多次堅定地向著前<br />\n一天清一天風雨飄　似了似了不了地了<br />\n他朝得到的縱是小　不緊要<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n心　亦天天的了　夢　天天的了<br />\n雖也未能料　但是我的決心<br />\n沒有點滴動搖　或且某月某日某宵<br />\n<br />\n有冇高手解詞？<br />\n我感覺似係講緊有夢想但係就一日拖一日唔實現 到最後發現就算係拖都好 夢想始終都冇放棄過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真正意思都係捉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩請高手解歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab4e8c0358cdb2051200b91fce3a463b0a0b793","tid":600062,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b77406869eafd0868f9030b23b89719f997aaa","tid":600062,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\